# Add FieldIdentifier Indexer handling

Add support for using expressions that resolve to indexers in `FieldIdentifier`.

## Description

To expand the capabilities of InputBase and its subsequent components in blazor, this pull request adds the ability to map an expression to an indexer, such that List or Dictionary entries can be referred to. Currently attempting to do so throws an ArgumentException.

Ex:
```cs
var listOfBools = new List<bool>();
```
```cshtml
@for(int i = 0; i < listOfBools.Length; i++) {
{
  <InputCheckbox @bind-Value="listOfBools[i]" />
}
```
